com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Interface ExtendedAttribute

public interface ExtendedAttribute

A representation of the model object 'Extended Attribute'. Structure for dynamic addition of attributes to a DeployModelObject.

Extended attribute instances are created using CoreFactory.createExtendedAttribute(). They are associated with a deploy object by being added to the list of DeployModelObject.getExtendedAttributes(). An extended attribute must have a name that is unique for the object.

The following features are supported:

  • Name

See Also:
CorePackage.getExtendedAttribute()
